continues.post_str: The undersigned is directed to pay that with effect from the 13th October 1995 Shri Cabinet Minister who has returned to Delhi after his medical treatment shall be Minister without Portfolio The Prime Minister shall continue to hold the charge of the Ministry of Railways for home more time
